summary:
18 September 2022 
I'll be jumping into the open water in Heusden to swim 2km in a bid to raise money in the fight against cancer. 
Feel free to sponsor me at https://www.fightcancer.nl/fundraisers/nickyeadie/swim-to-fight-cancer-heusden  every little helps!
